snippet.title: TeddyRoller1 Coming Soon
snippet.description:
First glimpse of Teddy Roller 1, an arcade experience where Teddy journeys his way to victory by passing through one gate after another.  The road is fraught with figures that try to knock Teddy of his ball. Balance is after all of utmost importance. 
#TeddyRoller #speedrun #steam #comingsoon #arcade #teddy #ball #unrealengine #indiegames #unreal
